name: Frank James
text: This place is great! They accept EBT Food and Cash benefits. The pizzas only take about 10 minutes to cook at home. If you want pizza this is the place to go. The prices are much better than other pizza places in town. Very friendly staff and customers. If you haven't had a pizza from Papa Murphy's... well, you better get on that!

name: Ada Rebecca Smith
text: Great pizza that is made exactly how we like it.

name: Mara Smith
text: Love this place!  Pizza is good, not all disgusting and greasy like with normal pizza places.  Do I care that I have to take it home and cook it?  Nope.  Who would complain about tasty smelling kitchens?
